data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $6000 IN BUYERS CLOSING COSTS TO HELP BUY DOWN THEIR RATE! Timeless two-story brick home proudly sits on an oversized lot in an established south side neighborhood. The lovely lawn lures you inside to an impressive soaring entry, extra large primary suite to the left, formal dining to the right, and large gathering room ahead, both of which connect to the bright kitchen and adjoining casual dining area offering outdoor access. Step outside to shade beneath a covered patio that overlooks the enormous yard with tasteful, mature landscaping, paved parking for all your extra vehicles or company, and... A POOL with soothing water feature. Plus, a sprinkler system and solar panels help spend less time working and more time playing! Once you've partied the day away, you'll appreciate the amenities upstairs: 3 additional bedrooms, another full bath, and second living room! If privacy, space, and convenience is what you seek, look no further!
